title: OTE Salem administrative office closed, Friday, July 3rd
text:
OTE Salem administrative office closed, Friday, July 3rd OTE Salem administrative office closed, Friday, July 3rd 
Posted on: July 2nd,   
In observance of Independence Day, the OTE main office in Salem on Liberty St SE will be closed this Friday, July 3, 2015. All 29 OTE rest area locations remain open and staffed. If you need emergency assistance at a rest area, please dial 9-1-1. All of us at OTE wish you a safe and happy Fourth of July holiday weekend. Share this post:
